abstract.text: A protocol that defines the methods provided by the host, so that a plug-in can query the timing properties of its input.

inlineContent.text: Using the FxTimingAPI, your plug-in can query the timing properties of its input image or images, image parameters, effect, timeline, and in or out points.
This version of the API is only available to plug-ins built in the FxPlug 4 style and later, and it intentionally doesnâ€™t inherit from previous versions.
